          "二十歳です。"
        ],
        "focus_examples_romaji": [
          "Indojin desu.",
          "Hatachi desu."
        ],
        "notes": "20 years old has an irregular reading: Hatachi (二十歳)."
      },
      "pronunciation": {
        "tips_en": [
          "Ensure 'sai' is pronounced like 'sigh', not 'say'."
        ],
        "tips_hi": [
          "सुनिश्चित करें कि 'sai' का उच्चारण 'साई' की तरह हो, 'से' नहीं।"
        ],
        "audio_ids": []
      },
      "examples": [
